<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係講事實<br />\n<br />\n事實就係公民黨提空置稅，個個正皮<br />\n而政府提空置稅，d人個個走出黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有d左膠林照英個d現象上面講左，籠門任搬<br />\n<br />\n有道理就駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好諗住轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb43575656c38a0a41329cd90398a1906522dcc7","tid":713873,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df141c007f45e591fc3f95b2c00fae2be21fe39","tid":713873,"uid":27617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"仲諗住會有d咩比較有質素既論述...<br />\n但睇完內文<br />\n常搵多半句分析都冇 數據又冇.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"以為經濟分析 原來玄學<br />\n呢樣野冇用 我另一個post 講過"},{"pid":"746dfcfb2c27049b4bfe566cb8c901a7b816595c","tid":713873,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c78ee5be8f498e6e2d2494f72611a1a8e6ed16b0","tid":713873,"uid":53186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:24:54.000Z","msg":"香港得一間地產商會特登空置D單位黎囤貨,就係恆隆(689大金主)<br />\n政府咁做應該係針對恆隆"},{"pid":"113472c926ba020f679f476c76765e7455f6c41b","tid":713873,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"轉嫁比買家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93468500ede3cf6669d9744772421ea6e7d31792","tid":713873,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb43575656c38a0a41329cd90398a1906522dcc7","tid":713873,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df141c007f45e591fc3f95b2c00fae2be21fe39","tid":713873,"uid":27617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2